msgid ""
"xref:web/webflux-webclient/client-attributes.adoc[Attributes] provide a "
"convenient way to pass information to the filter chain but they only "
"influence the current request. If you want to pass information that "
"propagates to additional requests that are nested, for example, via "
"`flatMap`, or executed after, for example, via `concatMap`, then you'll need "
"to use the Reactor `Context`."
msgstr ""

